                    <span>I was/am looking for a book on IP Routing. I can tell you this book is NOT for the beginner. It has no description on how IP addresses work or how subnets work. All it does is talk about the different protocols. This might be helpful once the reader understands the basics but not until then.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Uninteresting and doesn't cover much for the topic.</div>
